gameObject

Class MovableObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • gameObject.GameObject
      • gameObject.MovableObject
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Bomb, Enemy, Player, Projectile

    public abstract class MovableObject
extends GameObject
    Description:
    Overall MoveableObject that extends GameObject
    Utilizes methods that determines whether an object is capable of moving across a certain region
    Denotes the length and direction of an object's movement
    Since:
    2014-03-31
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Team 6
